I89. National Defense Stockpile Manager

I19(a) Appointment

I11The President shall designate a single Federal office to have responsibility for performing the functions of the President under this subchapter, other than under sections 98f(a)(1) and 98hÿ094 of this title. The office designated shall be one to which appointment is made by the President, by and with the advice and consent of the Senate.

