I21``In this Act:

I22``(1) T4Appropriate congressional committeesK._The term `appropriate congressional committees' means the Committee on International Relations [now Committee on Foreign Affairs] of the House of Representatives and the Committee on Foreign Relations of the Senate.

I22``(2) T4Government of sudanK._Except as provided in section 12, the term `Government of Sudan' means the National Islamic Front government in Khartoum, Sudan.

