I14(ii) the Director of National Intelligence; and

I14(iii) consistent with the Rules of the House of Representatives, the Standing Rules of the Senate, and Senate Resolution 400 of the 94th Congress or any successor Senate resolution_

I16(I) the congressional intelligence committees; and

I16(II) the Committees on the Judiciary of the House of Representatives and the Senate.

I79(3) Annual review

I18(A) Requirement to conduct

I13The head of each element of the intelligence community conducting an acquisition authorized under subsection (a) shall conduct an annual review to determine whether there is reason to believe that foreign intelligence information has been or will be obtained from the acquisition. The annual review shall provide, with respect to acquisitions authorized under subsection (a)_

