I89. Stockpile stewardship program

I19(a) Establishment

I11The Secretary of Energy, acting through the Administrator for Nuclear Security, shall establish a stewardship program to ensure_

I12(1) the preservation of the core intellectual and technical competencies of the United States in nuclear weapons, including weapons design, system integration, manufacturing, security, use control, reliability assessment, and certification; and

