I89. Program to monitor Department of Energy workers exposed to hazardous and radioactive substances

I19(a) In general

I11The Secretary shall establish and carry out a program for the identification and on-going medical evaluation of current and former Department of Energy employees who are subject to significant health risks as a result of the exposure of such employees to hazardous or radioactive substances during such employment.

