I12(9) Costs of promotional items and memorabilia, including models, gifts, and souvenirs.

I12(10) Costs for travel by commercial aircraft or by travel by other than common carrier that is not necessary for the performance of the contract and the cost of which exceeds the amount of the standard commercial fare.

