I67T1``SEC. 1005. COMPENSATION AND TRAVEL EXPENSES.

S5800

I21``(a) T4CompensationK._(1) Except as provided in paragraph (2), each member of the Commission may be compensated at not to exceed the daily equivalent of the annual rate of basic pay in effect for a position at level IV of the Executive Schedule under section 5315 of title 5, United States Code, for each day during which that member is engaged in the actual performance of the duties of the Commission under this title.

